Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,身体!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,温暖的身体!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:30.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:32.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回去吧 艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:33.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,天要黑了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:27.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙果然厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 又扔下我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.42,0:02:31.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不会让你跑掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:42.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 从昨天开始你就一直在赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:46.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去还没到目的地你就累趴下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:49.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小鬼现在怎样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉他那恶狠狠的眼神和倔强的性格跟格斯你很像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:54.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止急停!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:01.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要多为宿主着想一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这次又是什么妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.11,0:03:07.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一位老朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:12.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,别来无恙呢 挣扎者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:14.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是精灵吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:16.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你带著有趣的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:20.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦? 这个人似乎...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:24.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这种地方干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:30.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃向那些非人者寻仇之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:33.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾要前往之地有何物你自然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:36.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近有使徒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说 是元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:44.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神之手...那些家伙就在那里?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:49.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是也梦见了「光之鹰」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:51.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是启示
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:58.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以「鹰」为号的某人物将会出现在这尘世
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:02.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰...你是说鹰?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:06.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,羊群被引至沾满鲜血的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他们所追寻的希望乃是「光之鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,力场超过临界之时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本应存在于神之领域的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:16.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,会千年一度地受肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:22.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你和那位姑娘将会置身其中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:25.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,宛如旧日噩梦重演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.97,0:04:28.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蚀...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:32.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如蚀再临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:44.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说那情景...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:48.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那场景...会再次出现吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喜悦?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:57.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,凭人类的力量无法更改这个祭典的情节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会出现倒影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是由失去光芒的太阳所笼罩之地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,投射至遥远人世间的倒影罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说结果和那时候一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:12.38,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等出乎意料地在此地相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:13.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就是最好的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:17.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,吾等已在因果循环当中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:23.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么倒影 什么因果 我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我的确借助过你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我会凭自己的力量救她出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:41.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你身上的烙印会是你的救星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:45.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,给你一句忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一心不可二用!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 到底在想什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的团长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:27.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,拍那个摩兹古斯的马屁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:29.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是好佩服她的虔诚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:31.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 她会听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:40.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何那么愚钝的家伙能成为纹章官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是马屁拍得好呗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,话说又增加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.65,0:06:54.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么增加了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,难民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请...请问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:26.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩兹古斯大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一起过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也正要去礼拜堂找他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,令您受惊了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:34.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几个因为丑陋的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了残酷的迫害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:42.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被赶出了村子 城市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,作为妖怪人忌讳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至有因此逃进森林当野人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:54.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是天生的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:07:59.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这副面具的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我全身就会被烧得腐烂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那副样子恐怕...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...已经没个人形了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:15.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神啊 感谢您赐予我这次相遇的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被选中的命运之子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:21.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,自豪而虔诚地活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不喜欢这份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:27.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对伤害他人这种事情实在喜欢不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.15,0:08:30.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可即使如此我也为之自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:35.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是神赐予我的神圣职责
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:39.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是礼拜的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅弄出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:51.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在顶礼膜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.18,0:08:53.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:54.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚各做五百次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,五体投地这种膜拜方式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:02.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这十年间摩兹古斯大人从未有一天间断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎礼拜完了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是法尔纳塞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩兹古斯大人 您流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 让您见笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:22.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这座塔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:26.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以前关押着被霸王加尔塞利克幽禁的贤者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,据说他们在所有拷问中不断向神控诉王罪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.21,0:09:33.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,终于感动了上苍 令天使降临
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是灵验非凡的圣地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:40.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以令我下意识地大力礼拜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:42.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:46.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这伤害我几乎走不动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是不能周围跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:53.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但我很珍视这份痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的神圣使命是执行严格的神之律法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,或许应该为之感到悲哀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:03.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这会为许多人带来痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.66,0:10:06.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这伤对我来说既是惩戒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也是信仰的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么迷惑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:14.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:18.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务到底能否拯救民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:22.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,庶民对我们的风评满是恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:23.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不怕您笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们圣铁锁骑士团里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:28.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,也有不少人对这个任务持有异议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:32.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您可以把这番话当作是不成熟之人说的胡话尽情嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心这样下去只会一味让恐怖蔓延
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:39.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,让人心疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能因任务艰巨而叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.09,0:10:48.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不能质疑神明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:51.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,即便身心俱疲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,亦要一心一意 为了神而活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:58.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是所谓的信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所做的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:04.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,皆是为了神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:05.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.51,0:11:09.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆为了神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:12.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一切皆为了神!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老是承蒙你照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老奶奶 记得不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.71,0:11:40.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行啊 搞得浑身脏兮兮的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮...妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.81,0:11:47.89,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,约阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是什么身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:59.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你明知道但还是想上我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:00.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,客人!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你说再多的甜言蜜语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不能陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这...我并没有这个打算
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来上我啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:20.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:26.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的有那份勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚午夜钟声响起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:30.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在河边等你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大清早的嚷那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:04.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你爱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:06.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:11.10,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那你能跟我一起下地狱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:15.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:17.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,如果和你一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:32.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子 难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:21.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 我们下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.21,0:14:24.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 那个孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...幻觉?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 一起逃避吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰女神啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:53.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:04.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来 约阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,山羊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请帮他改宗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:17.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,来 喝了它你就是我们的一员了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,约阿希姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了那个男人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他想告密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这么高不可能活命了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 今天就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:50.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听到喧闹可能会有人来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:03.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你个骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:10.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐 你怎么在这
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:18.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来 不要过来啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:27.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你那是什么眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:33.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我从以前就讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,装作无所不知的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对他人摆出高高在上的面孔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:39.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好让自己感觉良好并沉没其中对吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:43.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不也跟我一样是个娼妇而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,为何能如此瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我大声叫唤的话同伴就会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你会被大卸八块的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:04.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:25.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.35,0:17:30.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个傻女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:34.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...将约阿希姆...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.55,0:17:36.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:40.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 她是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:43.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没记错的话 是妮娜那里的娼妇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是染病的疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:46.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:50.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:52.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:55.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 让我们看看那张腐烂的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:03.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把绷带解了一看美的简直让人想咬住不松口啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:06.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 闹吧闹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:08.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这才有乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:16.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,露加姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,饿死我了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,这是...怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:38.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.84,0:18:39.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:41.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:56.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦 你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:57.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:18:58.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她是魔女!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.40,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,点火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,服了那个女人 还真敢干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:02.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,团长家以前似乎是猎杀邪教徒的火刑场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小小年纪就开始放火了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被批准搜捕黑色剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.95,0:21:10.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎也是因为三年前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她在法王厅逮捕了企图发动叛乱的邪教徒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:17.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...并全部处予火刑的功绩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.83,0:21:20.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是经过千锤百炼的那啥(铁石心肠)啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.80,0:21:22.71,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然应该离她远点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:25.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的人 不准说闲话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.37,0:21:25.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:30.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是邪教徒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,邪教徒的儿子也是邪教徒!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:35.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要证明不是你就把火把扔过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.71,0:21:36.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.94,0:21:41.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,审问他父亲的时候已经调查清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:48.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是...是我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:49.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是想有恩于你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.87,0:22:05.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哟!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,没记错你是杰罗姆男爵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.46,0:22:13.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是纹章官 记性真好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:16.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不是那么坏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:17.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:19.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.34,0:22:20.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,很有骑士风范哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:22.36,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这件事事关我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.12,0:22:28.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也和那个孩子有相同的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:33.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的母亲也以邪教徒的罪名处予火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:36.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前 就在我的眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.62,0:22:41.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,三年前?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:06.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.53,0:23:07.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,给她祝福!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,请赐予她神明的祝福!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:23.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我没错!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.18,0:23:32.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那个头脑简单四肢发达的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,...我终于追上你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.86,0:23:50.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.86,0:23:09.20,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,她是个虔诚的孩子!
